longBusinessSummary: Taiwan Wax Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells refined wax in Taiwan and internationally. The company offers refined paraffin wax, microcrystalline wax, and light/heavy foots oil wax. It also trades in equipment and aquatic products; and offers brokerage services. The company was founded in 1987 and is based in Chiayi, Taiwan.
